<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700&family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/Reccoflix.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <title>Privacy Policy - ReccoFlix</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <%- include('partials/header') %>

            <div class="main-content-wrapper"
                style="min-height: 80vh; justify-content: flex-start; padding-top: 3rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; padding-right: 1.5rem;">
                <div style="max-width: 800px; text-align: left; color: #e0e0e0;">
                    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #fff; text-align: center;">Privacy Policy
                    </h1>

                    <div
                        style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><strong>Last Updated: January 2025</strong></p>
                        <p style="line-height: 1.6;">
                            Welcome to ReccoFlix. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal
                            information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when
                            you visit our website.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <h2
                        style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">
                        1. Information We
                        Collect</h2>
                    <p
                        style="line-height: 1.6; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">
                        - <strong>Account Information:</strong> When you register or log in via Google, we collect your
                        name and email address to create your profile.<br>
                        - <strong>Usage Data:</strong> We may collect information on how you interact with the site,
                        such as pages visited and anime added to your library.
                    </p>

                    <h2
                        style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">
                        2. How We Use
                        Your Information</h2>
                    <p
                        style="line-height: 1.6; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">
                        We use your information solely to:<br>
                        - Provide and maintain the Service.<br>
                        - Personalize your experience (e.g., your anime library).<br>
                        - Improve our website functionality.
                    </p>

                    <h2
                        style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">
                        3. Data Security
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        style="line-height: 1.6; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">
                        We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. However, please
                        note that no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
                    </p>

                    <div
                        style="margin-top: 3rem; text-align: center; font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.6;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">
                        Note: This is a portfolio project and not a commercial entity.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>